graphs.text: #   This page is contained in the innermost verso panel of a six-panel fold-out.
#   Two rows of veggies, top and bottom of page, 2 paras in between.
#   Plant [1,1] has "same" label as plant f102v2[3,4].
#   Quod videt.  The label is also similar to the container's label
#   on the bottom row of f89r1.
#   The label of plant [2,3] "opoldaiin" is similar to a title on page f1r,
# There are 4 names alternating with 3 plants.
# plant [1,2] - light roots, lumpy base of stem, dark leaf
# plant [1,3] - dark roots with claws?, dark leaves
# "U" transcription by J. Stolfi from scanned image.
# There are 4 labels alternating with 3 plants.
# plant [2,1] - large light roots, dark flowers
# plant [2,2]  - large light roots, dark shading?, dark inside flower
# plant [2,3] - long dark manifold roots, prickly dark leaves
